title: Watch, Chain, And Key, 1875–99
creditline: Gift of Mrs. John Innes Kane
description: Watch chain of ornamental links of gold and steel; at either end, a mailed fist holding ring with snakes head. Two ornaments; bust in armor on pedestal. Watch key with wolf's head on top.

tombstone.epitaph:
Watch, Chain, And Key, 1875–99.
1875–99. Gold, steel. Gift of Mrs. John Innes Kane. 1920-19-94-a/c.
